For version 3.11

Run to create config
oc cluster up --public-hostname=ec2-34-245-130-173.eu-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com --routing-suffix=ec2-34-245-130-173.eu-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com --base-dir=/openshift --write-config=true --skip-registry-check=true

Run to start
oc cluster up --public-hostname=ec2-34-245-130-173.eu-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com --routing-suffix=ec2-34-245-130-173.eu-west-1.compute.amazonaws.com --base-dir=/openshift --write-config=false --skip-registry-check=true

It then tries to connect to 127.0.0.1 somewhere
